{
  "id": "adv_event_2404_02_04",
  "title": "星見の海に\n消えた涙",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――魚魚っとさんがプロモーション大作戦を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after Gyogyo-tto-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.2177072644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "開始してしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "started Operation Promotion",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.2177072644,
      "endTime": 2.0131438851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "（私達はBIGGYOに手が届きかけていた）\n（でもプロモーション費用に大金を掛け過ぎた結果……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We were so close to reaching BIGGYO.）\n（But because we spent too much on promotion…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8464772202,
      "endTime": 11.9053206422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.3333332857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-gyogyo001.m4a",
      "text": "赤字がさらに酷いことになってしまったギョ……\nBIGGYOまであと一歩だというのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our deficit has gotten even worse‚ gyo…\nAlthough we were just one step away from BIGGYO…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3333332857,
      "endTime": 20.5890925249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.799998808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……魚魚っとさん、諦めないで下さい！\n私、みんなでBIGGYOになりたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way… Gyogyo-tto-san‚ don’t give up!\nI want to become BIGGYO with everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.799998808,
      "endTime": 30.6712916852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.8666654747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ！　ここで諦めたら……\n{user}さんも助けることが出来ません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! If we give up now…\nwe won’t be able to save {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8666654747,
      "endTime": 36.9934000175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "あなたのやり方に賛成出来ない部分もありましたが\n私達を思ってくれていたのは伝わってましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although I didn’t agree with some of your methods‚\nI know you were doing them for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.199998808,
      "endTime": 44.6124250889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.799998808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "出会った頃の勢いはどうしたんですか～？\n一度やるって決めたんだから、やり通しましょうよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What happened to the energy you had when we first met~?\nWe decided to do this‚ so let’s see it through!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.799998808,
      "endTime": 51.9069374562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.099998808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-gyogyo002.m4a",
      "text": "さくらギョン……琴乃ギョン……\nすずギョンにこころギョン……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-gyo… Kotono-gyo…\nSuzu-gyo and Kokoro-gyo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.099998808,
      "endTime": 57.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-gyogyo003.m4a",
      "text": "ギョギョギョ……君達には辛い思いをさせて\nしまったギョ……。責任はわしが取るギョ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyogyo… I’ve put you all through\nso much… I’ll take responsibility‚ gyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9999980927,
      "endTime": 69.04754924779999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12066.658226800002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12066.658226800002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12066.658226800002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.1333290896
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.0666563195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、魚魚っとさん！？　走ってどこ行くのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ Gyogyo-tto-san!? Where are you going?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0666563195,
      "endTime": 72.7489237946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The Next Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7333229861,
      "endTime": 74.7333229861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-gyogyo004.m4a",
      "text": "ギョギョギョ……？\nみんながわしを呼び出すなんてどうしたんだギョ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyogyo…?\nWhy have you all called me here‚ gyo…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7666537763,
      "endTime": 80.7935926916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで昨日まで赤字だったのに\n突然うちの事務所が黒字になってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were in the red until yesterday‚\nbut suddenly our office is in the black?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9999840578,
      "endTime": 86.98619707430001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、違法なお金とかじゃないですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn’t use illegal money‚ did you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1999840578,
      "endTime": 91.76209286059999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-gyogyo005.m4a",
      "text": "わしのヒレを売ったんだギョ。これを食べると不老不死\nになるとかならないとか……とても高価で希少だギョ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I sold my fin‚ gyo. It’s said that if you eat it‚ you gain immortality‚\nor something… It’s very expensive and rare‚ gyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1999927521,
      "endTime": 101.423507309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ヒ……ヒレなんて売って大丈夫なんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you sold your fin!? Is that okay?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6333184083,
      "endTime": 106.0045883973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "魚魚っとさん……ううっ……\n私達のために……うわぁぁぁん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyo-tto-san… Sniff…\nYou did it for us… Waaaaah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.199985075,
      "endTime": 117.962457037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-gyogyo006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなには沢山迷惑を掛けてすまなかったギョ……\n実はわしも小さい頃アイドルを目指してたギョ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry for causing you all so much trouble‚ gyo…\nActually‚ I dreamed of becoming an idol when I was little‚ gyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1666517417,
      "endTime": 127.20869256659999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-gyogyo007.m4a",
      "text": "だから君達と一緒に海中アイドルナンバーワンの称号\nBIGGYOを手に入れたかったんだギョ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I wanted to get the title of the number one\nunderwater idol‚ BIGGYO‚ gyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3999820232,
      "endTime": 134.4941092014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな大事なこと、早く教えて下さいよ……\nそうすれば……もっと何か出来たかもしれないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should’ve told us such an important thing sooner…\nIf you had… we might’ve been able to do something more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.6999789714,
      "endTime": 144.0106362818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "別に今からでも遅くないですよ！　BIGGYOまでは\nあと一歩なんですからライブでもすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not too late to start now! We’re just one step away\nfrom BIGGYO‚ so if we do a live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1999789714,
      "endTime": 152.0708407878,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8032.650756900011
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "魚魚っとさんが、魚魚っとさんが……\n魚魚っとさんが乾燥してきていますわ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyo-tto-san… Gyogyo-tto-san…\nGyogyo-tto-san is drying up!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.399976937,
      "endTime": 161.89521505049998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-gyogyo008.m4a",
      "text": "ギョギョ……そろそろ潮時ギョ……\nわしが地上で過ごせる時間は決まっていたギョ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyo… It’s about time‚ gyo…\nMy time on land was limited‚ gyo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.099976937,
      "endTime": 170.4949201743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_04-gyogyo009.m4a",
      "text": "本当はみんなともっと仲良くしたかった……\n今までお世話になったギョ……わしはもう……バタッ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really wanted to get closer to you all…\nThank you for everything‚ gyo… I… I'm… Thud.",
